The paper deals with inequalities related to divergences and learning problems, which are topics commonly studied in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and optimization, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) and cs.MA (mathematical optimization).
